This Program set up DataBase with below mentioned data and once requested gives the compounded result.

Prerequisites : mongodb , node js

Steps to start.
    1. run command 'npm install' to install all dependency 
    2. start mongodb server
    3. run command 'node ./src/test' to start the server 
    4. call http://localhost:3000/ from browser to get result 


DataBase Data:
[{
    title: "Vivo X50",
    category: "mobile",
    amount: 35000

},
